{"id":422,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":24,"title":"24. What did you do yesterday?","subtitle":"","level":"A2","parts":13,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/24-what-did-you-do-yesterday.422/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/24-what-did-you-do-yesterday-2022-03-07-21-12-15/0-24-what-did-you-do-yesterday.mp3","transcript":"Hi, how are you?\nYou look tired.\nDid you sleep okay last night?\nNo, I didn't.\nWhy? What did you do yesterday?\nI went to a nightclub last night and danced all night.\nOh, yeah? Did you have a good time?\nI had a wonderful time, but I'm beat today.\nWhat time did you leave the nightclub?\nI left at about 3:00 a.m.\nI'm not surprised that you're tired.\nWhich nightclub did you go to?\nFantastic. It's on Ontario Street. It's really nice.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:48:34","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Hi, how are you?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/24-what-did-you-do-yesterday-2022-03-07-21-12-15/1.mp3","time_start":2.57,"time_end":4.14},{"position":2,"content":"You look tired.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/24-what-did-you-do-yesterday-2022-03-07-21-12-15/2.mp3","time_start":4.14,"time_end":5.25},{"position":3,"content":"Did you sleep okay last night?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/24-what-did-you-do-yesterday-2022-03-07-21-12-15/3.mp3","time_start":5.25,"time_end":6.9},{"position":4,"content":"No, I didn't.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/24-what-did-you-do-yesterday-2022-03-07-21-12-15/4.mp3","time_start":6.9,"time_end":8.45},{"position":5,"content":"Why? What did you do yesterday?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/24-what-did-you-do-yesterday-2022-03-07-21-12-15/5.mp3","time_start":8.4